set oven to 450
boil for 10 minutes 

 - 12 lasagna

cook in skillet

 - 1/2 lbs sausage

set aside
add to same pan

 - 28 oz canned crushed tomatoes

bring to boil
boil until lasagna are cooked
place 1/2 cup cause in square pan
add sausage to sauce
layer lasagna and sauce
top with 

 - 200 g shredded mozzarella

cover with foil
bake until bubbly
remove foil
set oven to 350
bake 15 minutes
rest 15 minutes

#simple #italian
